	1.Enter a file name that does not exist
	Create new, save input content	
	
2.Enter a file that exists
	Ask user if add or overwrite	
	
3.Enter a file that exists with overwrite option
	Overwrite the new content, old content lost	
	
4.Enter a file that exists with add option	
	Ask user if add before or after
	
5.Enter a file that exists, add option, before		
	New content is saved before old content
		
6.Enter a file that exists, add option, after	
	New content is appended to old content